CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 20, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "They Don't Mind - April showers did not detract from the gaiety of these lassies as they wend their way to school. They are Christine Bradshaw and Estelle Joiner. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Christine Bradshaw and Estelle Joiner walking together underneath umbrella, on sidewalk with garages on left in background, and fire hydrant on right, another version
